{"tid":2114679,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"微軟承認Windows 10新Bug：錯誤顯示沒有網絡連接","createTime":"2020-07-19T04:32:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-31T13:50:39.000Z","uid":32577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"93df3af2abd90b42bc6960d0c7a18d56e475b83d","tid":2114679,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T04:32:40.000Z","msg":"現在，微軟方面已經證實，存在於Windows 10 May 2020（20H1/Version 2004）功能更新中的新問題&ndash;顯示錯誤的互聯網連接警告。<br />\n<br />\n根據用戶的反饋，在系統托盤中網絡狀態圖標上會出現黃色的三角形警告，並報告稱&ldquo;無法連接到網絡中&rdquo;。當你的設備正確連接到路由器的時候就有可能顯示該錯誤。<br />\n<br />\n儘管顯示這個錯誤的網絡連接警告，但是用戶依然可以在瀏覽器中正常訪問網頁。不過，Spotify、Cortana、Microsoft Store、Feedback Hub 等應用似乎都會根據 Windows 10 的網絡狀態才能訪問服務器。因此，當你出現虛假的網絡狀態報告的時候，Spotify 和其他應用程序可能無法正常工作。<br />\n<br />\n目前臨時的解決方案如下：<br />\n<br />\n打開Windows搜索<br />\n<br />\n查找 &ldquo;Registry Editor&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n打開 &ldquo;註冊表編輯器&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n導航到 &ldquo;HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE/SYSTEM/CurrentControlSet/Services/NlaSvc/Parameters/Internet&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n修改 &ldquo;EnableActiveProbing &ldquo;並將值從 &ldquo;0 &ldquo;改為 &ldquo;1&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n啟用ActiveProbing<br />\n<br />\n點擊 &ldquo;確定&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n關閉註冊表編輯器。<br />\n<br />\n重新啟動電腦。"},{"pid":"6f024f5706f13f8bddbc8cdd043ba9295acfcd8e","tid":2114679,"uid":281306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T04:33:56.000Z","msg":"windows係個笑話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"463a55e424a26382a6ed467c8e663da03fe1cfcb","tid":2114679,"uid":37136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T04:49:25.000Z","msg":"更新送bug<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1dc1493297a6d3635ae4d9aa3b95da66deaf86f","tid":2114679,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T05:37:38.000Z","msg":"洗鬼你認?<br />\n如田2Win10有一次更新係冇bug我仲驚"},{"pid":"9d7c16de03bbec0536ecfa74f807cff9e4144824","tid":2114679,"uid":57698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T13:50:39.000Z","msg":"跟住佢個解決方法整都解決唔到個問題 係咪要等到10月 11月更新先有可能解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}